              "free_text": [
                " A multiwire proportional counter, with an",
                "active area of 150 mm x 150 mm was placed at the",
                "focal plane of Heavy Ion Reaction Analyser. A mylar",
                "foil 0.5 um thick was used as the entrance window of",
                "the MWPC, which saparated the gas volume of MWPC (3",
                "mbar isobutane) from vacuum inside the HIRA."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two Silicon detectors were placed inside the",
                "target chamber at +/- 15.5 degree with respect to the",
                "beam direction in the horizontal plane to record",
                "Rutherford-scattered beam particles for absolute",
                "normalization of ER cross sections. To reset charge",
                "states of the evaporation residues a 30 ug/cm2 thick",
                "natC foil was placed 10 cm downstream from the target."
              ]
            }
